<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Loadbalancing on cdeclog</title><link>https://cdecl.github.io/tags/loadbalancing/</link><description>Recent content in Loadbalancing on cdeclog</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.155.1</generator><language>ko-kr</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 25 Oct 2021 00:00:00 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://cdecl.github.io/tags/loadbalancing/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Keepalived Basic</title><link>https://cdecl.github.io/devops/keepalived-basic/</link><pubDate>Mon, 25 Oct 2021 00:00:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://cdecl.github.io/devops/keepalived-basic/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Loadbalancing &amp;amp; High-Availability 를 위한 Keepalived 설정 및 테스트&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="keepalived"&gt;Keepalived&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.keepalived.org/"&gt;https://www.keepalived.org/&lt;/a&gt;{:target=&amp;quot;_blank&amp;quot;}&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;VRRP 를 활용 가상IP (VIP) 기반 서버 다중화 도구&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VRRP 는 여러 대의 라우터를 그룹으로 묶어 하나의 가상 IP 어드레스를 부여,&lt;br&gt;
마스터로 지정된 라우터 장애시 VRRP 그룹 내의 백업 라우터가 마스터로 자동 전환되는 프로토콜입니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
